title: Creating a new Clan
body: Hello every one! I am looking to create a community for OCE players! If any one is interested then post here ! Looking for staff to help build the place up!

replies.body: As long as its not a 100% full-time admin work kinda thing (I can hop on and help in the afternoon for a bit), I'm down for it.

You're Diamond. I'm like Silver elo.

Still, i'm famous.
